text: Maryamin (), also spelled Mreimin, may refer to: * Maryamin, Afrin, village in northern Aleppo Governorate, Syria * Maryamin, Homs, village in Homs Governorate, Syria * Maryamin, Idlib, village in Idlib Governorate, Syria * Maryamin, Jabal Seman, village in southern Aleppo Governorate, Syria
title: Maryamin
